      "rationale": "Material properties for Ti-6Al-4V ELI were drawn from ASTM F136 minimum guaranteed values supplemented by 15 tensile coupon tests from the production lot (mean E=114.2±2.1 GPa, σ_y=883±18 MPa). CoCr rod properties from manufacturer CoC (E=210 GPa, σ_y=690 MPa). Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of 5 production screws: outer diameter 7.502±0.018 mm, thread pitch 1.75±0.005 mm, core diameter 4.85±0.012 mm. UHMWPE block elastic modulus from 3 compression tests: E=0.94±0.08 GPa. All input distributions propagated via Latin hypercube sampling (n=500) to generate ensemble prediction intervals."
