      "rationale": "Eleven (N=11) experimental constructs were tested: 6 at Laboratory A (FDA/CDRH) and 5 at Laboratory B (DePuy Synthes), spanning two production lots (Lot 2021-A and Lot 2022-B). CMM dimensional verification confirmed all screws within drawing tolerance. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness: 3.8%; for yield force: 4.2%; for force at 40 mm: 5.1%. A one-way ANOVA found no statistically significant laboratory effect (p=0.31 for stiffness, p=0.27 for yield force), confirming reproducibility across sites. Production-representative assembly procedure followed per DePuy Synthes IFU."
    },
