      },
      "rationale": "Quantitative output comparison was performed for all three primary QoIs: stiffness (E/uval=1.42, 4.7% difference), yield force (E/uval=1.61, 6.4% difference), and force at 40 mm (E/uval=1.78, 5.7% difference). All E/uval values satisfy the <1.96 criterion; all percent differences satisfy the <10% criterion. FEA ensemble 95% prediction intervals encompass 11/11 (100%) of experimental observations for stiffness and yield force, and 10/11 (91%) for force at 40 mm. Full force-displacement curves (0–40 mm) were compared graphically; FEA ensemble band encompasses the experimental corridor throughout the loading history. Gradation 4 achieved due to the comprehensive quantitative and graphical comparison methodology."
